title: 01/11/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 01/11/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Wildcard in the NFL. How hurt the Steelers and Seahawks in their first round exits? What do the Browns need to do to get past the Chiefs next week? NBC's Chris Simms joins to look ahead at next week's matchups. Steelers Senior Writer for the Athletic Ed Bouchette joins us to discuss the future of the team. And former NFL QB Brady Quinn zooms in to preview tonight's College Football National Title game.
